      ],
      "notes": "This is a post-apocalyptic text adventure focused on exploration and environmental storytelling. Throughout the narrative, players encounter written references to people who have died prior to the events of the story. These include victims of an industrial accident, two individuals who have died by suicide while isolated, and a fire report describing a fatal house fire involving a child.\r\n\r\nIn later chapters, the story also references additional loss and hardship, including implied deaths from a collapsed apartment building, animals feeding on a dead deer, and a wounded woman who speaks with the player before passing away. The narrative includes moments where the player character and companions are injured, as well as the death of one of the protagonists.\r\n\r\nAll of these events are conveyed through non-graphic written descriptions. The game does not feature visual depictions of violence or active combat, and players do not initiate violent actions."
